text: WESE (92.5 FM), known as "92.5 The Beat", is an Urban Contemporary radio station based in Guntown, Mississippi, United States, and serves Tupelo and Northeast Mississippi with an ERP of 12,000 watts. WESE is owned by iHeartMedia, Inc., through licensee Capstar TX LLC. ==External links== * ESE Category:Urban contemporary radio stations in the United States Category:Radio stations established in 1982 Category:IHeartMedia radio stations
